"ngram\": \"frantic sightseeing\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1013}, {\"ngram\": \"the flame\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If only it could talk and give us its impressions.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"its impressions\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among other highlights, the flame was paraded by a beaming Thierry Henry while jogging down the Champs-Elys\\u00e9es.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1140, \"end\": 1153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thierry Henry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\"}, {\"begin\": 1177, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"score\": 0.9992163039517089, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Champs-Elys\\u00e9es\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Champs-\\u00c9lys\\u00e9es\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other highlights\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"the flame\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was later held high by Paris ballerinas from Bastille to the Louvre museum, where the former \\u00e9toile dancer of the Paris Op\\u00e9ra, Marie-Claude Pietragalla, took it to see the Mona Lisa and Delacroix's Liberty Leading the People.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.796911644109585e-40, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\