s' lives after months, if not years, of works in the streets of the capital in preparation for the Games.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A welcome interlude\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1974}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisians' lives\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"works\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 2065, \"to\": 2076}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Parisians needed it, and badly.\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's so good to smile again,\\\" said the waiter at caf\\u00e9 Saint Regis on the tip of the \\u00cele Saint-Louis, overlooking Notre-Dame's flying buttresses.\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the waiter\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"caf\\u00e9\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2178}, {\"ngram\": \"Saint Regis\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"the tip\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00cele Saint-Louis\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2224}, {\"ngram\": \"Notre-Dame's flying buttresses\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France's rail network hit by 'massive arson attack' delaying Eurostar trains hours before Paris Olympics opening ceremony Olympics 2024: Paris erects ring of steel in bid to thwart threats to security Olympics 2024: A Games on a spectacular scale - but is Paris ready to party?\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2271, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.63295380182465