uting and avoid 11 metro stations which are now closed (some of them until October).\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2635, \"end\": 2637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999943119735568, \"rank\": 5.68798800920196e-06, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Time\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2608}, {\"ngram\": \"date\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"The last few weeks\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"many Parisians\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2695}, {\"ngram\": \"de\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"11 metro stations\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not to mention entire bridges closed to the traffic, and sometimes even to pedestrians, transformed as they are into rows of tiered seats for the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"entire bridges\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"the traffic\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2880}, {\"ngram\": \"pedestrians\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"rows\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"tiered seats\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2966}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 2991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The traffic at crossroads is often so intense that Parisians have had to wait for at least 30 minutes to hop on their bus, instead of the usual five.\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3142, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The traffic\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"crossroads\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3018}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"at least 30 minutes\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3094}, {\"ngram\": \"their bus\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One thing in particular has irritated them to no end: having to walk for milesas if caged in, behind 6ft fences- 44,000 of them to be precise.\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One thing\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3152}, {\"ngram\": \"no end\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3195}, {\"ngram\": \"milesas\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It looks like a prison,\\\" said a small child as I attempted to find an exit somewhere along the Rue du Cardinal Lemoine in the 5th arrondissement.\", \"from\": 3286, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a prison\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3309}, {\"ngram\": \"a small child\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3330}, {\"ngram\": \"an exit\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3361}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rue\", \"from\": 3378, \"to\": 3385}, {\"ngram\": \"du Cardinal Lemoine\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3405}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5th arrondissement\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3431}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody had been warned it seems, not even local mayors, such as Jean-Pierre Lecoq of the very chic 6th arrondissement, who discovered them one morning like everybody else.\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3497, \"end\": 3508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dardenne_brothers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.111927849208188e-19, \"text\": \"Jean-Pierre\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dardenne_brothers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dardenne_brothers\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 3433, \"to\": 3439}, {\"ngram\": \"the very chic 6th arrondissement\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3550}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had never been told,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3638, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Parisians with buggies and in wheelchairs have had a particularly tough time on the now fenced pavements.\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3649}, {\"ngram\": \"buggies\", \"from\": 3655, \"to\": 3662}, {\"ngram\": \"wheelchairs\", \"from\": 3670, \"to\": 3681}, {\"ngram\": \"a particularly tough time\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3716}, {\"ngram\": \"the now fenced pavements\", \"from\": 3720, \"to\": 3744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shopkeepers and caf\\u00e9 owners are also impacted.\", \"from\": 3746, \"to\": 3792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3762, \"end\": 3766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5742856805223334e-41, \"text\": \"caf\\u00e9\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shopkeepers\", \"from\": 3746, \"to\": 3757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Caf\\u00e9 terraces behind bars are not exactly inviting, are they?\\\"\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Caf\\u00e9 terraces\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3807}, {\"ngram\": \"bars\", \"from\": 3815, \"to\": 3819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"says a waiter in Rue Dauphine.\", \"from\": 3857, \"to\": 3887, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a waiter\", \"from\": 3862, \"to\": 3870}, {\"ngram\": \"Rue Dauphine\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not to mention receiving deliveries.\", \"from\": 3888, \"to\": 3924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"deliveries\", \"from\": 3913, \"to\": 3923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And since July 18, the heart of the city, where the opening ceremony will be taking place, is a \\\"grey zone\\\", forbidden to all unless you live there and have a pass.\", \"from\": 3926, \"to\": 4090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 3936, \"to\": 3940}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 3954}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 3958, \"to\": 3966}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 3974, \"to\": 3994}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 4010, \"to\": 4015}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"grey zone\", \"from\": 4020, \"to\": 4032}, {\"ngram\": \"a pass\", \"from\": 4083, \"to\": 4089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Needless to say caf\\u00e9 and restaurant owners and shopkeepers are in despair, most of them closed for at least a week, and those still open have the greatest difficulty getting deliveries.\", \"from\": 4091, \"to\": 4276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4107, \"end\": 4111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5742856805223334e-41, \"text\": \"caf\\u00e9\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coffeehouse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"shopkeepers\", \"from\": 4138, \"to\": 4149}, {\"ngram\": \"despair\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4164}, {\"ngram\": \"at least a week\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 4205}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest difficulty\", \"from\": 4233, \"to\": 4256}, {\"ngram\": \"deliveries\", \"from\": 4265, \"to\": 4275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will get compensation, of course, just like during Covid.\", \"from\": 4277, \"to\": 4339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"compensation\", \"from\": 4291, \"to\": 4303}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4314}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid\", \"from\": 4333, \"to\": 4338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is France after all.\", \"from\": 4340, \"to\": 4363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4346, \"end\": 4352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6329538018246503e-15, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Did I also mention the ugly 5G antennas at every corner, the 65 giant screens, 1,137 portable loos and 169 sound amplifiers?\", \"from\": 4364, \"to\": 4488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ugly 5G antennas\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4403}, {\"ngram\": \"every corner\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4419}, {\"ngram\": \"the 65 giant screens\", \"from\": 4421, \"to\": 4441}, {\"ngram\": \"1,137 portable loos\", \"from\": 4443, \"to\": 4462}, {\"ngram\": \"169 sound amplifiers\", \"from\": 4467, \"to\": 4487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is the first time the Olympic Games are organised in the heart of a city, and it may be the last!\", \"from\": 4489, \"to\": 4590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 4496, \"to\": 4510}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4528}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 4546, \"to\": 4555}, {\"ngram\": \"a city\", \"from\": 4559, \"to\": 4565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Honestly, if this does not wreck Paris, I'd be surprised\\\" Philippe, a teacher at Jussieu university, told me, sombrely.\", \"from\": 4591, \"to\": 4710, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4624, \"end\": 4629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.796911644109585e-40, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4672, \"end\": 4679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jussieu_Campus\", \"score\": 0.9999999934934749, \"rank\": 6.455042121997941e-09, \"text\": \"Jussieu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jussieu_Campus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jussieu_Campus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\" Philippe\", \"from\": 4647, \"to\": 4657}, {\"ngram\": \"a teacher\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will avoid the Games at all costs.\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4725, \"to\": 4734}, {\"ngram\": \"all costs\", \"from\": 4738, \"to\": 4747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, except for sport addicts who managed to get tickets at an affordable price (which must be an Olympic discipline in itself), I do not know one Parisian who will stay for the Games.\", \"from\": 4750, \"to\": 4937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport addicts\", \"from\": 4769, \"to\": 4782}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 4802, \"to\": 4809}, {\"ngram\": \"an affordable price\", \"from\": 4813, \"to\": 4832}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic discipline\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4869}, {\"ngram\": \"one Parisian\", \"from\": 4896, \"to\": 4908}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4927, \"to\": 4936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not out of loathing for them, more out of fear that something may not go exactly as planned, and perhaps, just like people abroad, they want to see the beautiful competitions on television where the view is always superb and the close ups on the action unbeaten.\", \"from\": 4938, \"to\": 5206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"loathing\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 4963}, {\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 4986, \"to\": 4990}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4996, \"to\": 5005}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5060, \"to\": 5066}, {\"ngram\": \"the beautiful competitions\", \"from\": 5092, \"to\": 5118}, {\"ngram\": \"television\", \"from\": 5122, \"to\": 5132}, {\"ngram\": \"the view\", \"from\": 5139, \"to\": 5147}, {\"ngram\": \"the action unbeaten\", \"from\": 5186, \"to\": 5205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They want to enjoy the Games without the daily logistical hassle and the back kitchen horrors.\", \"from\": 5208, \"to\": 5302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 5227, \"to\": 5236}, {\"ngram\": \"the daily logistical hassle\", \"from\": 5245, \"to\": 5272}, {\"ngram\": \"the back kitchen horrors\", \"from\": 5277, \"to\": 5301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, all is not doom and gloom.\", \"from\": 5304, \"to\": 5339, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"doom\", \"from\": 5324, \"to\": 5328}, {\"ngram\": \"gloom\", \"from\": 5333, \"to\": 5338}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The wonders of theOlympicsare often found in small and unexpected details.\", \"from\": 5340, \"to\": 5414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The wonders\", \"from\": 5340, \"to\": 5351}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsare\", \"from\": 5355, \"to\": 5369}, {\"ngram\": \"small and unexpected details\", \"from\": 5385, \"to\": 5413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last week, Parisians crossing the river could see the river brigade and subaquatic security forces (yes, there is such a thing) performing mock operations.\", \"from\": 5415, \"to\": 5570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parisians\", \"from\": 5426, \"to\": 5435}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 5445, \"to\": 5454}, {\"ngram\": \"the river brigade\", \"from\": 5465, \"to\": 5482}, {\"ngram\": \"subaquatic security forces\", \"from\": 5487, \"to\": 5513}, {\"ngram\": \"such a thing\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5541}, {\"ngram\": \"mock operations\", \"from\": 5554, \"to\": 5569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speed boats fitting only six special agents each were having the time of their lives, or so it looked to all perched on the bridge, intrigued by their risky manoeuvres.\", \"from\": 5571, \"to\": 5739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Speed boats\", \"from\": 5571, \"to\": 5582}, {\"ngram\": \"only six special agents\", \"from\": 5591, \"to\": 5614}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 5632, \"to\": 5640}, {\"ngram\": \"their lives\", \"from\": 5644, \"to\": 5655}, {\"ngram\": \"the bridge\", \"from\": 5691, \"to\": 5701}, {\"ngram\": \"their risky manoeuvres\", \"from\": 5716, \"to\": 5738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going at high speed, they rehearsed jumping on barges and big boats in choreographed rescue operations.\", \"from\": 5740, \"to\": 5843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high speed\", \"from\": 5749, \"to\": 5759}, {\"ngram\": \"barges\", \"from\": 5787, \"to\": 5793}, {\"ngram\": \"big boats\", \"from\": 5798, \"to\": 5807}, {\"ngram\": \"choreographed rescue operations\", \"from\": 5811, \"to\": 5842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will not only have to deal with potential terrorist threats but also save enthusiastic members of the public who might accidentally fall into the water.\", \"from\": 5844, \"to\": 6001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"potential terrorist threats\", \"from\": 5881, \"to\": 5908}, {\"ngram\": \"enthusiastic members\", \"from\": 5923, \"to\": 5943}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 5947, \"to\": 5957}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 5991, \"to\": 6000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There will be 30 expert divers and 30 river rescuers at all times present by the banks.\", \"from\": 6002, \"to\": 6089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"30 expert divers\", \"from\": 6016, \"to\": 6032}, {\"ngram\": \"30 river rescuers\", \"from\": 6037, \"to\": 6054}, {\"ngram\": \"all times\", \"from\": 6058, \"to\": 6067}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 6079, \"to\": 6088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, after much agonising about the possibility of swimming in the Seine, and \\u20ac1.4 billion spent since 2015 to build colossal filtering stations, treatment plants and storm basins, Paris mayor Anne Hidalgo finally fulfilled her promise and dived into the Seine last Wednesday.\", \"from\": 6091, \"to\": 6367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6158, \"end\": 6163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.069441841130315e-39, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 6272, \"end\": 6277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 