to\": 6565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One lives in hope.\", \"from\": 6568, \"to\": 6586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 6581, \"to\": 6585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Allez, \\\"Vive les Jeux!\\\"\", \"from\": 6587, \"to\": 6610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6604, \"end\": 6608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jeux\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeux\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Allez\", \"from\": 6587, \"to\": 6592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 6612, \"to\": 7490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6672, \"end\": 6681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999999765705072, \"rank\": 1.5078720972996397e-08, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 6772, \"end\": 6781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999999765705072, \"rank\